page.title: 10Katey, Sherburn-in-Elmet.
page.content: Hello! My name is Katey Burke. I am 10 years old.I live in the village of Sherburn-in-Elmet.I wake up at 7.30 in the morning by an alarm clock.This has a bell.I go downstairs for breakfast.I have a piece of toast which is burnt bread.I set off for school at 8.40 on my bicycle,which is a way of transport I learn different subjects like Art, Maths.and English.I start school at 9.15 until 3.30.We have dinner at school which is dry or cooked.When I get home I watch television.T.V. is a screen which you watch different pictures on.I then have my tea which is sandwiches with cottage cheese filling.I go swimming for 2 hours.My father takes me in the car.My favourite is breaststroke,but I have to do exercises to keep fit as well.I return at 9.00.I read for 30 minutes before I fall asleep.
